WEBVTT

00:10:30.440 --> 00:10:33.880
the difficulty of his job

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:37.736
before he would enter
the sanctity of his home.

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:40.536
(Music)

00:10:40.560 --> 00:10:42.536
AG: If you're more of an integrator,

00:10:42.560 --> 00:10:44.680
you're perfectly happy
to mix work and home.

00:10:45.520 --> 00:10:49.416
In one study, Nancy found that integrators
were more satisfied and committed

00:10:49.440 --> 00:10:52.000
when their organizations
offered on-site child care.

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:55.800
But segmentors had
a strikingly different reaction.

00:10:56.760 --> 00:11:01.096
NR: The menu of options
didn't really help for segmentors.